      <odd id="aspace_b3289d4e0b2dfefb554c2796b9f5d0f3">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 24-E (YRG 24-E), Records of departments, offices, programs, and projects of the Yale School of Forestry.</p>  
      </odd>
