         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>School of Forestry and Environmental Studies, Yale University, Records Concerning the Industrial Forestry Seminar (RU 44). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_cb136dddcf106944acb2395821f92935">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged in two series: I. Industrial Forestry Seminar Records, 1955-1979. II. Seminar Instructors, 1955-1971.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_3c60e861a20a4bdee62dd7bd23511041">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of papers and materials from seminars and files from seminar instructors documenting the Industrial Forestry Seminar conducted by the Yale School of Forestry and Environmental Studies (called the School of Forestry prior to 1972).</p>  
      </scopecontent>
